<h2>Objective</h2>
<p>
Improve operational clarity, reduce reliance on informal knowledge,
and support consistent execution through better documentation.
</p>

<h2>Key Findings</h2>
<ul>
<li>Core procedures were not centrally maintained</li>
<li>Documentation was outdated in some areas</li>
<li>Ownership of process updates was unclear</li>
</ul>

<h2>Recommendations</h2>
<ul>
<li>Build a central process library</li>
<li>Assign document owners for maintenance</li>
<li>Review procedures on a regular schedule</li>
</ul>

<h2>Skills Demonstrated</h2>
<p>
Process design, workflow documentation,
operational support planning, and policy alignment.
</p>

